    pivotx/y:  750.0 x  750.0
    bbox_x/y:  750.0 x  250.0
    offset  :    0.0 x  500.0
    offsetpx:    0.0 x   19.0
    Tile px :   18.9 x   19.0

    DIAMOND1: PATD   55DIAMOND1VLINCON0000000000022500225002250043130112500093
    tile px : W  75.0 x H 143.8
    bbox_   : X1125.0 x Y  93.0
